-- Chez Clement Restaurant Chain Up for Sale, Figaro Says
-- B y   M e l i s s a   P o z s g a y
-- 2012-08-07T05:31:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-07/chez-clement-restaurant-chain-up-for-sale-figaro-says.html
The Freres Blanc group is selling its
Chez Clement chain of 11 restaurants in Paris, Le Figaro
reported without citing its sources. Investment bank Easton is
handling the sale, and there are two industrial buyers
interested, the newspaper said.  Freres Blanc and Chez Clement both declined to comment, Le
Figaro said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Melissa Pozsgay in Paris at 
 mpozsgay@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
